>Speaking of which, Gu Nan had also met the God of Labyrinths when he was playing the game, and David certainly did not look this miserable back then.</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block54" type="h6"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-aje12" style="line-height:1.5;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:13px"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px">The God of Labyrinths was dressed in tattered clothes, and his face was covered in dirt and grime, as if he was a beggar who had wandered for a long time.</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block55" type="h6"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-47pph" style="line-height:1.5;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:13px"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px">"You <em>are</em> David, right? Your appearance…"</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block56" type="h6"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-euf90" style="line-height:1.5;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:13px"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px">"Your Excellency Gu Nan." David revealed a bitter smile. "I'm afraid I can only appear like this for the near future… I accidentally offended that one from Mist Town."</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block57" type="h6"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-brimk" style="line-height:1.5;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:13px"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px">Gu Nan instantly understood when he heard that and laughed. "You offended Diana? Your courage is commendable."</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block58" type="h6"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-9fu2d" style="line-height:1.5;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:13px"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px">God of Poverty Diana, one of the Three Sisters of Misery. Offending her was equal to being cursed by the God of Poverty, the God of Decline, and the God of Misfortune at the same time.</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block59" type="h6"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-d6pp3" style="line-height:1.5;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:13px"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px">David, the God of Labyrinths, was famous for his ability to attract aggro. He could always offend people no matter where he went. So as soon as Gu Nan saw his name, he knew that this one must have come to take refuge.</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block60" type="h6"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-cm0on" style="line-height:1.5;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:13px"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px">"You want to join the Heaven-God Alliance?" Gu Nan asked bluntly without beating around the bush.</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block61" type="h6"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-8nd2l" style="line-height:1.5;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:13px"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px">"Yes, Your Excellency." David straightened his clothes, making himself look barely presentable.</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block62" type="h6"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-63age" style="line-height:1.5;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:13px"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px">"This humble one has long heard of your noble organization's impressive reputation, and—"</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block63" type="h6"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-8ucfi" style="line-height:1.5;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:13px"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px">"Alright, drop the flattery," Gu Nan interrupted. He didn't believe that this fellow, who was always terribly busy all year round, would know much about the Heaven-God Alliance.</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block64" type="h6"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-a2dls" style="line-height:1.5;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:13px"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px">While speaking, he brought out Karina's divine spear again.</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block65" type="h6"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-69npq" style="line-height:1.5;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:13px"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px">"These two spear shafts are stained with the blood of the first Blacksmith God. Help me find the source of the blood, and the Heaven-God Alliance will be able to protect you."</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block66" type="h6"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-b7tle" style="line-height:1.5;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:13px"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px">David's face stiffened. "The first generation Blacksmith God—that was during the First Great War. It would take an unimaginable amount of divine power to find him…"</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block67" type="h6"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-1h3fj" style="line-height:1.5;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:13px"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px">Gu Nan tapped his arm with a broken spear. "You'll lose all your divine power if you can't find him."</span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block68" type="h6"></div><div class="QHjDE rzoRKE" id="viewer-74tqq"><div class="gO6aa y8JqQg y8JqQg h1LxM HkHlcQ HkHlcQ"><div class="_4-MIc dhz2rt" data-hook="divider-single"><div class="pFxyb"><svg class="B70rH _3JsO2 Athvf D8R-x"><line x2="100%" y1="1" y2="1"></line></svg><div class="Ia90Q"> </div></div></div></div></div><div data-hook="rcv-block69" type="divider"></div><h6 class="ZGnlH Y9Dpf OZy-3 lnyWN yMZv8w bCMSCT public-DraftStyleDefault-block-depth0 fixed-tab-size public-DraftStyleDefault-text-ltr" id="viewer-e1khp"><span class="B2EFF public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr"><span style="font-size:18px"><br role="presentation"/></span></span></h6><div data-hook="rcv-block70" type="empty-line"></div><div class="QHjDE rzoRKE" id="viewer-52g7o"><div class="eVgRH jKKp9 xE7K3m xE7K3m z2rFB"><a class="_0te7W" data-hook="buttonViewer" href="https://phoenixtls.wixsite.com/phoenixtl/post/chapter-425-entrusting" rel="noopener noreferrer" role="button" style="border:0px solid blue;color:#f4f5f1;backgr